# cogninode runs in LOCAL mode (BYOK key, no backend) when these are unset.
# Set both to boot MANAGED mode: Clerk sign-in, Convex backend, per-user
# OpenRouter keys + credits. `npx convex dev` fills VITE_CONVEX_URL into
# .env.local automatically.
#
# VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://your-deployment.convex.cloud
# VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...

# ── Convex deployment env vars (set in the Convex dashboard, NOT here) ──
# CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN   Clerk Frontend API URL (JWT template "convex")
# CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET      svix secret for the clerk-users-webhook endpoint
# OPENROUTER_MANAGEMENT_KEY management key from openrouter.ai/settings/management-keys
# RAZORPAY_KEY_ID           Razorpay key id (publishable; returned to client)
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET       Razorpay key secret (orders API + checkout HMAC)
# RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET   secret of the /razorpay-webhook endpoint
# USD_PER_CREDIT            optional, default 0.0005
# STARTER_CREDITS           optional, default 100
# PACK_INR                  optional, default 300
# PACK_CREDITS              optional, default 3000
